{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I just have to mention that on that day-- and the others, who-- who didn't fall down, who were not on stretchers-- their numbers were all called out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they all went to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Ebensee was the camp where-- the-- the absolute, the most cruel SS men were there, hitting people with whips, and sticks, and metal bars, and the rifle butt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a steady supply.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could kill 3,000 a day, because a fresh 3,000 kept coming from the other camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it doesn't matter how many-- [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Carry the cement, and push this, and take the bricks in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were building, extending, the factories inside the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were building work benches, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the conditions were there horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know because one of my friends came back-- one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told me that everybody around him died, all his friends, all my friends and his friends, died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the situation there was that the camp was about 6 or 8 kilometers from the workplace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And where they slept, they slept in a tent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is just interruption of my story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I have to tell his story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think it's very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Where-- where they slept, in a tent, there was no food whatsoever-- no breakfast, and no bread, and no soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you could only get soup or a piece of bread, if you went the 8 kilometers to the tunnel, to the workplace.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you worked there your eight or 10 hours, then you had a chance to get some cabbage soup or beetroot soup.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you stayed at home-- they didn't mind if you stay at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
